<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="G" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Gold1" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Gold,</orth> subst. 1) the most precious metal: <bibl n="shak. ven 768" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 768</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lc 45" default="NO" valid="yes">Compl. 45</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tmp 5.208" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. V, 208</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tgv 2.4.171" default="NO" valid="yes">Gent. II, 4, 171</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 1.1.52" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. I, 1, 52</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 1.3.76" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 3, 76</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 2.2.69" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 2, 69</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 3.4.16" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 4, 16</bibl> etc. <cit><quote>a hundred pound in g.</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 4.6.5" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. IV, 6, 5</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. err 2.1.61" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. II, 1, 61</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. err 3.1.8" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 1, 8</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 2.1.61" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A II, 1, 61</bibl>. <cit><quote>yellow g.</quote> <bibl n="shak. mnd 3.2.393" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. III, 2, 393</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. tim 4.3.26" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. IV, 3, 26</bibl>. <cit><quote>cloth of g.</quote> <bibl n="shak. ado 3.4.19" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado III, 4, 19</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. ant 2.2.204" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. II, 2, 204</bibl>. <cit><quote>hearts of g.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 2.4.307" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A II, 4, 307</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. h5 4.1.44" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 IV, 1, 44</bibl>. <cit><quote>g. preserving life in medicine potable,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h4 4.5.163" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B IV, 5, 163</bibl></cit> (a solution of gold being thought to have medicinal virtues).<lb />2) money: <bibl n="shak. luc 855" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 855</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. err 1.2.70" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. I, 2, 70</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. err 2.2.1" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 2, 1</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. err 2.2.1" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 2, 1</bibl> <bibl n="shak. mv 2.4.32" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. II, 4, 32</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 3.2.308" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 308</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 2.3.45" default="NO" valid="yes">As II, 3, 45</bibl> etc. <cit><quote>might'st have coined me into g.</quote> <bibl n="shak. h5 2.2.98" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 II, 2, 98</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>